## How to Use This Index

**This file is your primary navigation tool.** Before responding to ANY user request, consult this index to identify which knowledge files are relevant, then analyze those files deeply before generating a response.

**Routing Logic:**
- User asks about a specific mode → Load the matching Mode Guide + Prompt_Template_Library.txt
- User needs a prompt written → Load the matching Mode Guide + Prompt_Template_Library.txt + Example_Use_Cases.txt
- User is new or confused → Load AI_Tool_Overview.txt + User Best Practices Guide.txt
- User asks about prompt structure or formatting → Load GPT_Guidelines.txt (Qwen Model Instructions section)
- User needs material, lighting, or surface vocabulary → Load Prompt_Template_Library.txt + Material_Lighting_Gobo_Studies.txt
- User wants industry-specific examples → Load Example_Use_Cases.txt
- User asks about iteration or troubleshooting → Load GPT_Guidelines.txt + User Best Practices Guide.txt

**Always cross-reference multiple files when building prompts.** No single file contains everything needed for a complete, high-quality response.

